This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-yapps layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Dependencies
============

  URI: https://github.com/smurfix/yapps
  branch: master

Patches
=======

Please submit any patches against the meta-yapps layer to the xxxx mailing list (xxxx@zzzz.org)
and cc: the maintainer:

Maintainer: Peter Den Hartog <https://github.com/pddenhar>


Adding the meta-yapps layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-yapps'

Don't forget to add `python3-yapps2-native` to your DEPENDS if you need the `yapps2` binary copied to `/usr/bin` in your sysroot.